managegroups.py is a script for remotely managing VCL user groups. It uses VCL&rsquo;s XML RPC API to provide an easy command line driven way of doing group management.
{color:#ff0000}{}NOTE: This script does not work with python 2.7. It relies on the xmlrpclib module which changed from 2.6 to 2.7 in a way that broke the script. You need to use python 2.6 for it to work.{color}

Download information managegroups.py is not included in any official releases.

